Break Glass Access – Emergency AWS Login System (Per‑Account Model) 

 

Overview 

Break Glass Access is an emergency login method used only when AWS SSO is unavailable. Each AWS account (Prod, Shared, VDI, Network) contains its own local IAM break‑glass users. 

 

Break‑glass access is: 

Restricted 

MFA‑enforced 

Fully monitored 

Enabled/disabled by the break‑glass admin 

Use it only during real emergencies. 

 

